data.title: Register of Licensed Property Services Providers
data.meta_description:
Current Licence Holders - Register Compiled 23/08/2024  

"Licence Type" relates to the Property Service which the Licensee is licensed to provide. There are four different types, namely: 

Licence Type A - The Auction of Property other than Land 

Licence Type B - The Purchase or Sale, by whatever means, of Land
